1
00:00:00,680 --> 00:00:02,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was wondering, Shio and Akari...</font>

2
00:00:02,790 --> 00:00:05,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you two think about Eiyu?</font>

3
00:00:09,590 --> 00:00:11,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why the sudden question?</font>

4
00:00:11,620 --> 00:00:12,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously.</font>

5
00:00:13,030 --> 00:00:15,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sudden? Well, because Eiyu—</font>

6
00:00:15,750 --> 00:00:20,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's still mistaken about us dating.</font>

7
00:00:20,370 --> 00:00:21,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Haru, over here!</font>

8
00:00:23,920 --> 00:00:26,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told you to stay out of this!</font>

9
00:00:26,880 --> 00:00:29,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? I just wanted to help out!</font>

10
00:00:29,740 --> 00:00:31,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just watch over us, okay?</font>

11
00:00:32,140 --> 00:00:34,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know you wanna know, too.</font>

12
00:00:35,010 --> 00:00:37,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I don't!</font>

13
00:00:37,890 --> 00:00:41,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In any case, don't ever bring it up again!</font>

14
00:00:41,860 --> 00:00:43,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fine.</font>

15
00:00:56,370 --> 00:01:01,500
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Arial"><font size="24"><b><font color="#0f100d">You Can't Be in a <font color="#29e1ef">Ro<font color="#ee3c51">m-<font color="#953db6">Co<font color="#f5a309">m <font color="#0f100d">with
Your Childhood Friends!</font></font></font></font></font></font></b></font></font></b></font>

16
00:02:15,020 --> 00:02:16,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry about that!</font>

17
00:02:16,990 --> 00:02:19,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's going on, you two?</font>

18
00:02:19,130 --> 00:02:21,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, nothing. Don't worry about it.</font>

19
00:02:21,540 --> 00:02:25,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But this really feels 
like old times, doesn't it?</font>

20
00:02:25,880 --> 00:02:29,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We always used to bring snacks 
to share, remember?</font>

21
00:02:29,230 --> 00:02:31,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just play it off for now.</font>

22
00:02:31,240 --> 00:02:33,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, we did!</font>

23
00:02:33,380 --> 00:02:37,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Remember how we made 
the losers play the Pocky Game?</font>

24
00:02:37,470 --> 00:02:39,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, I do!</font>

25
00:02:39,110 --> 00:02:42,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You and I kissed for real one time!</font>

26
00:02:42,090 --> 00:02:43,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bleh! So gross!</font>

27
00:02:43,930 --> 00:02:45,190
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font color="#7f81e6"><font size="40"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b>CRACK</b></font></font></font></b></font>

28
00:02:43,930 --> 00:02:45,190
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font color="#7f81e6"><font size="40"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b>CRACK</b></font></font></font></b></font>

29
00:02:44,050 --> 00:02:45,190
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font color="#7f81e6"><font size="40"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b>CRACK</b></font></font></font></b></font>

30
00:02:45,190 --> 00:02:46,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And then...</font>

31
00:02:46,320 --> 00:02:47,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Haru, that's a touchy subject!</font>

32
00:02:47,850 --> 00:02:49,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, whoops!</font>

33
00:02:49,190 --> 00:02:51,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, a kiss, huh?</font>

34
00:02:51,440 --> 00:02:53,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A real kiss...</font>

35
00:02:53,190 --> 00:02:56,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But hey, look! They're getting jealous! 
You've got a chance!</font>

36
00:02:56,260 --> 00:02:59,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think they're more 
disappointed than jealous.</font>

37
00:02:59,700 --> 00:03:04,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-Well, it happened when we were kids, 
so it doesn't count. Right?</font>

38
00:03:04,770 --> 00:03:06,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, exactly!</font>

39
00:03:06,270 --> 00:03:10,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Plus, it was with Eiyu! 
It was far from romantic!</font>

40
00:03:11,350 --> 00:03:13,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure, we "kissed," 
but it was just for a second.</font>

41
00:03:13,420 --> 00:03:16,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And we bumped teeth, so it hurt!</font>

42
00:03:16,020 --> 00:03:18,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seriously wasn't anything special!</font>

43
00:03:18,670 --> 00:03:20,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cut it out! That's too graphic!</font>

44
00:03:21,210 --> 00:03:22,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Th-This is hell!</i></font>

45
00:03:22,870 --> 00:03:24,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh yeah.</font>

46
00:03:24,430 --> 00:03:26,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Someone gave this to us as a souvenir.</font>

47
00:03:26,660 --> 00:03:28,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wanna try some octopus rice crackers?</font>

48
00:03:28,690 --> 00:03:31,600
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="20"><font color="#d26064">Smooch Smooch</font></font></b></font>

49
00:03:28,690 --> 00:03:34,420
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="20"><font color="#b06766">Octopus Rice Crackers</font></font></b></font>

50
00:03:28,690 --> 00:03:35,440
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="10"><font color="#dfd7d3">So Good,
You'd Want to Kiss It!</font></font></b></font>

51
00:03:29,480 --> 00:03:32,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Smooch, smooch, 
octopus rice crackers"...</font>

52
00:03:32,500 --> 00:03:35,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"So good you'd want to kiss it!"</font>

53
00:03:35,440 --> 00:03:35,810
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Impact"><b><font size="40"><font color="#dc22c7">M</font></font></b></font></b></font>

54
00:03:35,810 --> 00:03:36,190
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Impact"><b><font size="40"><font color="#dc22c7">ME</font></font></b></font></b></font>

55
00:03:36,190 --> 00:03:36,570
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Impact"><b><font size="40"><font color="#dc22c7">MEN</font></font></b></font></b></font>

56
00:03:36,570 --> 00:03:36,940
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Impact"><b><font size="40"><font color="#dc22c7">MENA</font></font></b></font></b></font>

57
00:03:36,940 --> 00:03:37,320
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Impact"><b><font size="40"><font color="#dc22c7">MENAC</font></font></b></font></b></font>

58
00:03:37,290 --> 00:03:39,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Someone, help!</i></font>

59
00:03:37,320 --> 00:03:37,690
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Impact"><b><font size="40"><font color="#dc22c7">MENACI</font></font></b></font></b></font>

60
00:03:37,690 --> 00:03:39,700
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Impact"><b><font size="40"><font color="#dc22c7">MENACING</font></font></b></font></b></font>

61
00:03:39,700 --> 00:03:41,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm back!</font>

62
00:03:41,660 --> 00:03:43,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! Do we have guests?</font>

63
00:03:43,660 --> 00:03:44,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Runako!</i></font>

64
00:03:44,970 --> 00:03:46,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just in time!</font>

65
00:03:46,310 --> 00:03:48,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See? It's Haru! Remember Haru?</font>

66
00:03:50,960 --> 00:03:53,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Runako! How many years has it been?</font>

67
00:03:53,650 --> 00:03:54,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh my gosh!</font>

68
00:03:54,960 --> 00:03:57,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've grown so big, Runako!</font>

69
00:03:58,970 --> 00:04:02,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No!</font>

70
00:04:03,970 --> 00:04:05,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No!</font>

71
00:04:05,580 --> 00:04:06,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Runako?!</font>

72
00:04:06,730 --> 00:04:09,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm scared of frogs! I'm scared of frogs!</font>

73
00:04:09,450 --> 00:04:10,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Frogs?</font>

74
00:04:10,730 --> 00:04:14,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was traumatized 
by Haru-kun way back.</font>

75
00:04:15,250 --> 00:04:19,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kero-chan, Kero-chan, Kero-Kero-Kero-chan.</font>

76
00:04:19,810 --> 00:04:21,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ribbit, ribbit.</font>

77
00:04:21,030 --> 00:04:22,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Runako!</font>

78
00:04:22,730 --> 00:04:24,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Haru-kun!</font>

79
00:04:25,520 --> 00:04:28,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I brought you something cool!</font>

80
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:30,000
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font color="#303a38">ribbit</font></b></font>

81
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:30,000
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font color="#303a38">ribbit</font></b></font>

82
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:30,000
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font color="#464845">wriggle</font></b></font>

83
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:30,000
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font color="#464845">wriggle</font></b></font>

84
00:04:31,500 --> 00:04:34,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You love frogs, right, Runako?</font>

85
00:04:34,050 --> 00:04:36,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No... Just Kero-chan...</font>

86
00:04:36,930 --> 00:04:38,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, give it some love!</font>

87
00:04:40,260 --> 00:04:43,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Slimy! Gross! Slimy! Gross!</font>

88
00:04:43,260 --> 00:04:44,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Runa—</font>

89
00:04:53,770 --> 00:04:57,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#000000">No!</font></font>

90
00:05:01,150 --> 00:05:04,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I really thought 
she'd like it at the time.</font>

91
00:05:04,530 --> 00:05:07,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry, Runako. I really am.</font>

92
00:05:09,290 --> 00:05:10,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I said I'm sorry!</font>

93
00:05:10,820 --> 00:05:13,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't run, Runako!</font>

94
00:05:10,820 --> 00:05:13,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Frogs! I'm scared of frogs!</font>

95
00:05:13,970 --> 00:05:15,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get away from me!</font>

96
00:05:15,240 --> 00:05:16,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told you, I'm sorry!</font>

97
00:05:16,800 --> 00:05:18,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Stay away!</font>

98
00:05:17,290 --> 00:05:20,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I feel bad for Runako, 
but she helped me big time.</i></font>

99
00:05:18,060 --> 00:05:18,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Runako!</font>

100
00:05:18,900 --> 00:05:19,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}No!</font>

101
00:05:19,750 --> 00:05:20,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Wait up!</font>

102
00:05:20,740 --> 00:05:23,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not mentally prepared for this!</font>

103
00:05:23,010 --> 00:05:24,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa! Whoops!</font>

104
00:05:51,400 --> 00:05:53,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">D-Does this not count either?</font>

105
00:05:57,790 --> 00:06:01,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yeah, please don't count this.</font>

106
00:06:02,060 --> 00:06:05,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I-I'm exhausted...</i></font>

107
00:06:10,520 --> 00:06:11,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bye!</font>

108
00:06:10,600 --> 00:06:13,230
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Comic Sans MS"></font></b><font color="#dc9a98">Bye</font></font>

109
00:06:11,230 --> 00:06:13,230
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Comic Sans MS"></font></b><font color="#dc9a98">See ya!</font></font>

110
00:06:11,280 --> 00:06:13,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Damn it, they're totally fine!</i></font>

111
00:06:11,280 --> 00:06:13,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}See ya!</font>

112
00:06:13,610 --> 00:06:16,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And I'm over here, freaking out!</i></font>

113
00:06:18,160 --> 00:06:20,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They kissed... they kissed...</i></font>

114
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:23,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They... kissed...</i></font>

115
00:06:24,310 --> 00:06:26,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Haru-kun, too?</i></font>

116
00:06:26,830 --> 00:06:29,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Does Haru-kun also...?!</i></font>

117
00:06:32,010 --> 00:06:35,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Haru-kun, I envy you.</i></font>

118
00:06:40,590 --> 00:06:43,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was no big deal back then.</font>

119
00:06:58,500 --> 00:06:59,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"Kiss"!</i></font>

120
00:06:58,890 --> 00:06:59,400
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Arial Black"><font size="40"><font color="#f5ebef">Kisu</font></font></font></b></font>

121
00:07:01,280 --> 00:07:02,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"Kiss"!</i></font>

122
00:07:01,650 --> 00:07:02,150
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="40"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#d86d90">Kisu</font></font></font></b></font>

123
00:07:05,200 --> 00:07:06,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Kiss!</i></font>

124
00:07:06,940 --> 00:07:09,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't stop thinking about it!</i></font>

125
00:07:20,540 --> 00:07:23,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Does Haru-kun have feelings for Eiyu?</i></font>

126
00:07:23,250 --> 00:07:25,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! You good?!</font>

127
00:07:25,740 --> 00:07:27,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, yes.</font>

128
00:07:27,550 --> 00:07:29,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! Shio?</font>

129
00:07:30,770 --> 00:07:31,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Haru-kun...</font>

130
00:07:31,790 --> 00:07:33,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing?</font>

131
00:07:33,770 --> 00:07:35,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You scared me.</font>

132
00:07:36,260 --> 00:07:37,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just tripped.</font>

133
00:07:37,930 --> 00:07:39,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're so clumsy.</font>

134
00:07:39,660 --> 00:07:41,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right, well, be careful!</font>

135
00:07:47,720 --> 00:07:49,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Haru-kun.</font>

136
00:07:49,440 --> 00:07:51,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can I join you?</font>

137
00:07:54,650 --> 00:07:56,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Want me to slow down?</font>

138
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:57,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm okay!</font>

139
00:07:57,710 --> 00:07:58,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's the spirit!</font>

140
00:07:58,940 --> 00:08:01,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're totally different from Eiyu!</font>

141
00:08:01,960 --> 00:08:02,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eiyu?</font>

142
00:08:02,960 --> 00:08:06,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We played one-on-one the other day, 
and he couldn't move at all.</font>

143
00:08:06,970 --> 00:08:10,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I teased him, his face went 
completely red, I couldn't help but laugh.</font>

144
00:08:13,220 --> 00:08:15,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you... have feelings?</font>

145
00:08:15,920 --> 00:08:16,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For what?</font>

146
00:08:17,650 --> 00:08:19,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm talking about Eiyu.</font>

147
00:08:20,380 --> 00:08:21,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

148
00:08:21,540 --> 00:08:23,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You seemed happy when you kissed him.</font>

149
00:08:24,360 --> 00:08:26,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What?!</font>

150
00:08:26,490 --> 00:08:29,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you talking about? 
Of course not!</font>

151
00:08:30,090 --> 00:08:34,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I bet you're the one who likes him,
since you're so worried.</font>

152
00:08:35,370 --> 00:08:37,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm right, huh?</font>

153
00:08:38,670 --> 00:08:40,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, Shio!</font>

154
00:08:40,100 --> 00:08:41,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't tell you!</font>

155
00:08:41,680 --> 00:08:44,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! You'll run out of breath 
if you go too fast!</font>

156
00:08:48,580 --> 00:08:49,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come to think of it,</font>

157
00:08:49,890 --> 00:08:53,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you used to say, "It's not fair 
you're always playing with Haru-kun"!</font>

158
00:08:54,290 --> 00:08:57,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's our turn to play with you!</font>

159
00:08:57,640 --> 00:09:00,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're jealous of me, aren't you?</font>

160
00:09:01,660 --> 00:09:04,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm the one he held hands with first!</font>

161
00:09:04,650 --> 00:09:05,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

162
00:09:05,660 --> 00:09:10,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The first one to take a bath, fight, 
and share spoons with him was all me!</font>

163
00:09:10,190 --> 00:09:12,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not jealous at all!</font>

164
00:09:12,660 --> 00:09:14,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on. You're getting all worked up!</font>

165
00:09:14,740 --> 00:09:17,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Am not! <i>You're</i> the one 
getting worked up!</font>

166
00:09:17,160 --> 00:09:18,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

167
00:09:18,030 --> 00:09:20,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've been running with all your might!</font>

168
00:09:21,030 --> 00:09:23,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is my usual pace!</font>

169
00:09:23,540 --> 00:09:25,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your usual?! That's stupid!</font>

170
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:26,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut up!</font>

171
00:09:31,090 --> 00:09:34,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why don't you just admit it already?</font>

172
00:09:35,090 --> 00:09:36,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right back atcha.</font>

173
00:09:37,660 --> 00:09:41,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In my case, I'm his childhood friend.</font>

174
00:09:42,230 --> 00:09:45,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm his childhood friend, too.</font>

175
00:09:49,190 --> 00:09:53,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jeez, it's not like that.</font>

176
00:09:57,330 --> 00:10:00,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">D-Does this not count either?</font>

177
00:10:03,020 --> 00:10:04,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shio?</font>

178
00:10:04,330 --> 00:10:06,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're drenched in sweat!</font>

179
00:10:06,110 --> 00:10:08,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing out this early?</font>

180
00:10:08,660 --> 00:10:10,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">U-Um, nothing really.</font>

181
00:10:10,940 --> 00:10:12,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How about you?</font>

182
00:10:12,140 --> 00:10:13,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm about to have break—</font>

183
00:10:14,340 --> 00:10:15,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa.</font>

184
00:10:17,430 --> 00:10:19,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-Thanks.</font>

185
00:10:19,080 --> 00:10:21,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, whoa... Are you okay?</font>

186
00:10:44,960 --> 00:10:46,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-Sorry...</font>

187
00:10:47,160 --> 00:10:48,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have to go take a bath.</font>

188
00:10:48,880 --> 00:10:50,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See ya!</font>

189
00:10:50,130 --> 00:10:51,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

190
00:10:51,210 --> 00:10:52,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See ya.</font>

191
00:10:55,320 --> 00:11:00,030
