00:10:58,970 --> 00:11:01,970
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="20"><font size="28"><font color="#eff1f3">KISS</font></font></font></b></font>

194
00:11:00,030 --> 00:11:02,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's like an angel's kiss</i></font>

