00:11:01,970 --> 00:11:02,970
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="40"><font color="#eff1f3">KISS</font></font></b></font>

196
00:11:03,880 --> 00:11:04,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Kiss.</i></font>

197
00:11:04,020 --> 00:11:06,480
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}</b><font size="24"><font color="#e6e9e5">Kiss</font></font></font>

