201
00:11:11,480 --> 00:11:12,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Kiss.</i></font>

202
00:11:11,900 --> 00:11:14,740
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}</b><font size="32"><font color="#e6e9e5">Kiss</font></font></font>

203
00:11:12,740 --> 00:11:14,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Onii-chan, you keep dropping your food.</font>

204
00:11:15,060 --> 00:11:18,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Please watch out for "akisu" this season.</i></font>

205
00:11:16,610 --> 00:11:18,740
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}</b><font size="40"><font color="#e6e9e5">Kiss</font></font></font>

206
00:11:18,750 --> 00:11:20,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You did it again!</font>

207
00:11:20,780 --> 00:11:21,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Huh?</i></font>

208
00:11:22,390 --> 00:11:25,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We just kissed... right?</i></font>

209
00:11:26,000 --> 00:11:27,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We did, right?</i></font>

210
00:11:27,560 --> 00:11:30,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is this really gonna turn into a rom-com?!</i></font>

211
00:11:31,080 --> 00:11:32,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Onii-chan?</font>

212
00:11:39,250 --> 00:11:40,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's been two days...</i></font>

213
00:11:40,990 --> 00:11:42,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I wonder...</i></font>

214
00:11:43,190 --> 00:11:45,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I wonder how she's been feeling...</i></font>

215
00:11:46,400 --> 00:11:50,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I mean, how am I supposed to 
act when I see her?</i></font>

216
00:11:50,950 --> 00:11:53,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Do I look presentable?</i></font>

217
00:11:54,150 --> 00:11:56,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>All right! Good!</i></font>

218
00:11:56,030 --> 00:11:58,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Morning, Eiyu!</font>

219
00:11:58,830 --> 00:12:00,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shi...o?</font>

220
00:12:00,660 --> 00:12:02,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-Hey, morning.</font>

221
00:12:02,280 --> 00:12:03,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're not going inside?</font>

222
00:12:04,790 --> 00:12:06,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, the teacher's coming!</font>

223
00:12:07,640 --> 00:12:09,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Morning, everyone!</font>

224
00:12:11,290 --> 00:12:13,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, did you do your homework?</font>

225
00:12:13,500 --> 00:12:14,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sakai!</font>

226
00:12:14,570 --> 00:12:15,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not fair!</font>

227
00:12:15,750 --> 00:12:17,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You two sure are close!</font>

228
00:12:17,420 --> 00:12:19,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Well...</font>

229
00:12:20,940 --> 00:12:23,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Yeah, yeah. And also...</font>

230
00:12:21,760 --> 00:12:22,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Huh?</i></font>

231
00:12:23,670 --> 00:12:24,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Huh?</i></font>

232
00:12:25,930 --> 00:12:27,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Huh?!</i></font>

233
00:12:27,950 --> 00:12:30,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Shio, so...</font>

234
00:12:30,390 --> 00:12:32,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can we t-talk after...</font>

235
00:12:32,510 --> 00:12:35,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right! We're going home now!</font>

236
00:12:36,580 --> 00:12:38,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See ya!</font>

237
00:12:38,250 --> 00:12:39,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O-Okay.</font>

238
00:12:40,470 --> 00:12:43,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Huh? </i>Huh<i>?!</i></font>

239
00:12:45,350 --> 00:12:49,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Runako!</font>

240
00:12:52,960 --> 00:12:54,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Runako!</font>

241
00:12:54,200 --> 00:12:55,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you going home, too?</font>

242
00:12:55,430 --> 00:12:56,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Didn't expect to run into you!</font>

243
00:12:56,680 --> 00:12:58,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eek! Please let me go!</font>

244
00:12:58,520 --> 00:13:00,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm getting goosebumps! Goosebumps!</font>

245
00:13:00,340 --> 00:13:01,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, come on!</font>

246
00:13:01,940 --> 00:13:03,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's rewrite your memories...</font>

247
00:13:03,090 --> 00:13:04,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No! Please stay away from me!</font>

248
00:13:04,680 --> 00:13:06,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">with fun... ones...</font>

249
00:13:05,350 --> 00:13:06,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}No!</font>

250
00:13:08,710 --> 00:13:10,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, isn't that Eiyu?</font>

251
00:13:10,850 --> 00:13:13,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But something feels off.</font>

252
00:13:14,530 --> 00:13:16,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His back's wide open!</font>

253
00:13:16,870 --> 00:13:19,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kiss... kiss...</font>

254
00:13:19,150 --> 00:13:20,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know we kissed for sure.</font>

255
00:13:20,360 --> 00:13:24,370
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="8"><font color="#9c9495">A girl friend kissed me</font></font></b></font>

256
00:13:20,360 --> 00:13:24,370
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="15"><font color="#767071">A Girl Suddenly Kissed You?!</font></font></b></font>

257
00:13:20,360 --> 00:13:24,370
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="15"><font color="#767071">The Psychology Behind It and How to Handle It</font></font></b></font>

258
00:13:20,690 --> 00:13:23,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why's she acting like nothing happened?</font>

259
00:13:24,370 --> 00:13:26,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did it mean nothing to her?!</font>

260
00:13:26,230 --> 00:13:27,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

261
00:13:27,370 --> 00:13:29,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! What are you two doing?!</font>

262
00:13:30,120 --> 00:13:31,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, uh...</font>

263
00:13:31,400 --> 00:13:33,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Never mind that, Onii-chan.</font>

264
00:13:33,070 --> 00:13:34,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you reading about k-kissing?!</font>

265
00:13:34,990 --> 00:13:36,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, um...</font>

266
00:13:36,380 --> 00:13:37,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this about the other day?</font>

267
00:13:37,730 --> 00:13:40,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You said it didn't count!</font>

268
00:13:40,020 --> 00:13:40,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

269
00:13:40,580 --> 00:13:43,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Onii-chan... Don't tell me 
you like Haru-kun!</font>

270
00:13:44,550 --> 00:13:45,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, you dummy!</font>

271
00:13:45,910 --> 00:13:47,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This isn't about Haru!</font>

272
00:13:47,640 --> 00:13:48,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

273
00:13:48,450 --> 00:13:50,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-It's not about me?!</font>

274
00:13:50,550 --> 00:13:52,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a relief.</font>

275
00:13:53,770 --> 00:13:55,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then...</font>

276
00:13:55,100 --> 00:13:56,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who kissed you?</font>

277
00:13:56,710 --> 00:13:58,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who was it?</font>

278
00:13:58,370 --> 00:14:01,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was someone besides me, right?</font>

279
00:14:01,010 --> 00:14:04,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you're looking it up, 
then it must've been recent.</font>

280
00:14:04,460 --> 00:14:05,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No! Stop!</font>

281
00:14:05,610 --> 00:14:06,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was nothing!</font>

282
00:14:07,300 --> 00:14:08,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know! It was Akari, right?</font>

283
00:14:08,820 --> 00:14:09,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?!</font>

284
00:14:09,790 --> 00:14:11,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You <i>were </i>talking
about her the other day!</font>

285
00:14:11,530 --> 00:14:12,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No! It's not!</font>

286
00:14:12,790 --> 00:14:14,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was Shio!</font>

287
00:14:14,920 --> 00:14:16,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">N-No! Not Shio!</font>

288
00:14:17,200 --> 00:14:18,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, cold <i>shou</i>-lder!</font>

289
00:14:18,930 --> 00:14:21,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My friend got the 
cold shoulder from a girl!</font>

290
00:14:22,130 --> 00:14:24,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your <i>friend</i>?</font>

291
00:14:24,040 --> 00:14:28,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You seem pretty emotionally 
invested, looking things up.</font>

292
00:14:28,940 --> 00:14:30,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-That's because...</font>

293
00:14:31,310 --> 00:14:35,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He said a girl friend of his 
kissed him out of nowhere,</font>

294
00:14:35,260 --> 00:14:39,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but then she acted like nothing happened
the next time they saw each other.</font>

295
00:14:39,820 --> 00:14:43,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was curious about what it meant.</font>

296
00:14:44,070 --> 00:14:46,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She wouldn't kiss him 
if she didn't like him!</font>

297
00:14:46,640 --> 00:14:50,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just hold her close and kiss her back!</font>

298
00:14:51,340 --> 00:14:53,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-Wh-What? Are you kidding me?</font>

299
00:14:53,190 --> 00:14:54,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait a minute!</font>

300
00:14:54,830 --> 00:14:59,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doing that without making sure you 
both like each other is just gross!</font>

301
00:14:59,460 --> 00:15:01,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't get it.</font>

302
00:15:01,240 --> 00:15:03,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Momentum is key 
in this kind of situation!</font>

303
00:15:03,400 --> 00:15:04,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're wrong!</font>

304
00:15:04,380 --> 00:15:06,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Feelings matter most!</font>

305
00:15:06,190 --> 00:15:08,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have to verbalize them first!</font>

306
00:15:08,050 --> 00:15:09,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, you two.</font>

307
00:15:10,890 --> 00:15:12,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you think, Onii-chan?</font>

308
00:15:13,120 --> 00:15:15,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you have feelings for Shio-chan?</font>

309
00:15:15,980 --> 00:15:17,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

310
00:15:17,460 --> 00:15:19,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you do, then you have to tell her!</font>

311
00:15:19,760 --> 00:15:21,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're her childhood friend!</font>

312
00:15:21,570 --> 00:15:23,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, this is about my <i>friend</i>...</font>

313
00:15:23,170 --> 00:15:24,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It doesn't matter!</font>

314
00:15:24,600 --> 00:15:27,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Momentum! Momentum is especially key 
when it comes to childhood friends!</font>

315
00:15:27,270 --> 00:15:27,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

316
00:15:27,860 --> 00:15:30,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Quit overthinking and just go for it!</font>

317
00:15:30,600 --> 00:15:31,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No!</font>

318
00:15:31,390 --> 00:15:33,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have to communicate, Onii-chan!</font>

319
00:15:33,500 --> 00:15:34,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Do I have feelings...</i></font>

320
00:15:36,040 --> 00:15:40,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>for my childhood friends?</i></font>

321
00:15:41,840 --> 00:15:44,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I don't know!</font>

322
00:15:44,060 --> 00:15:48,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't imagine being in a real rom-com 
with my childhood friends!</font>

323
00:15:49,900 --> 00:15:52,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whine, whine, whine, whine.</font>

324
00:15:52,510 --> 00:15:56,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're on your way to 
being rejected by everyone!</font>

325
00:15:58,930 --> 00:16:02,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I might get annoyed too 
if you keep acting like that.</font>

326
00:16:02,650 --> 00:16:04,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, we agree on something!</font>

327
00:16:04,850 --> 00:16:06,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It doesn't mean anything!</font>

328
00:16:08,780 --> 00:16:11,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They're annoyed... by me...</i></font>

329
00:16:13,880 --> 00:16:16,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>To make a decision...</i></font>

330
00:16:16,660 --> 00:16:18,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and just go for it...?</i></font>

331
00:16:20,420 --> 00:16:22,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No way, that sounds terrifying!</i></font>

332
00:16:23,420 --> 00:16:27,170
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#b0b0c9">Sports Day
Executive
Committee
Team</font></font></b></font>

333
00:16:24,550 --> 00:16:27,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyone want to take on this role?</font>

334
00:16:28,380 --> 00:16:30,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll do it!</font>

335
00:16:31,500 --> 00:16:33,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then, the second person will be...</font>

336
00:16:34,670 --> 00:16:36,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'll do it!</font>

337
00:16:38,560 --> 00:16:41,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These two are this year's sports day 
executive committee members.</font>

338
00:16:41,810 --> 00:16:42,560
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="18"><font face="Arial Black"><font color="#e890ce">clap</font></font></font></b></font>

