00:16:41,810 --> 00:16:42,560
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Arial Black"><font color="#e890ce">clap</font></font></b></font>

340
00:16:41,810 --> 00:16:42,560
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="18"><font face="Arial Black"><font color="#e890ce">clap</font></font></font></b></font>

341
00:16:42,920 --> 00:16:45,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've got this, Eiyu!</font>

342
00:16:45,320 --> 00:16:46,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yeah...</font>

343
00:16:49,300 --> 00:16:52,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa! There's a lot of equipment!</font>

344
00:16:52,250 --> 00:16:53,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yeah...</font>

345
00:16:54,500 --> 00:16:58,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder if we'll finish 
inspecting them all today.</font>

